 the Blue &amp; Gold — Sanjivani University Football Club.\"/><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&amp;family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"antialiased font-sans bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 flex flex-col min-h-screen\"><header class=\"fixed top-0 inset-x-0 z-50 h-16 flex items-center transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent border-b border-transparent\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 w-full flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm group-hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-4 h-4 text-white\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"hidden sm:block leading-tight\"><div class=\"font-display text-[17px] tracking-widest transition-colors text-brand-blue border-brand-blue/20\">SANJIVANI FC</div><div class=\"text-[9px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase transition-colors text-slate-500\">University Football</div></div></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"relative px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200\n                    text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-blue\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"relative px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200\n                    text-brand-blue\" href=\"/about\">About<span class=\"absolute bottom-1 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue\"></span></a><a class=\"relative px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200\n                    text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-blue\" href=\"/squad\">Squad</a><a class=\"relative px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200\n                    text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-blue\" href=\"/coach\">Coach</a><a class=\"relative px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200\n                    text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-blue\" href=\"/matches\">Matches</a><a class=\"relative px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200\n                    text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-blue\" href=\"/gallery\">Gallery</a><a class=\"relative px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200\n                    text-slate-600 hover:text-brand-blue\" href=\"/virtual-pitch\">Pitch</a><a class=\"btn-blue ml-2 text-xs !px-4 !py-2 shadow-none\" href=\"/recruit\">Join Us</a></nav><button id=\"mobile-menu-btn\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation\" class=\"md:hidden w-9 h-9 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-colors\n              bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-200\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-4 h-4\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"min-h-screen pt-16\"><div style=\"opacity:1;transform:none\"><!--$--><div><section class=\"relative h-64 flex items-end overflow-hidden bg-white border-b border-slate-200\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50/50 via-white to-slate-50\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(#003087 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:24px 24px\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 w-full pb-10\"><div style=\"opacity:1;transform:none\"><p class=\"label-sm mb-2 text-brand-blue\">Our Journey</p><h1 class=\"heading-section text-4xl md:text-5xl text-slate-900\">A New Era of Football</h1></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-24 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-start\"><div><div class=\"section-divider\"></div><h2 class=\"heading-section mb-6\">A New Chapter</h2><div class=\"space-y-5 text-slate-600 font-medium text-[15px] leading-relaxed\"><p>Sanjivani University Football Club is more than just a team; it is a movement. Founded in 2025, we are building a world-class football culture that merges high-level athletic performance with academic rigor.</p><p>We aren&#x27;t looking for just any players. We are looking for <strong>pioneers</strong>—individuals who want to be the first to lift trophies, the first to set records, and the first to establish a legacy that will last for generations.</p><p>Under the tactical leadership of Head Coach Neha Koli, Sanjivani FC is starting from a blank slate. This is your chance to write the first page of our history. Whether you are an experienced national-level athlete or a hidden talent on campus, there is a place for those with the heart of a champion.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-0 relative\"><div class=\"absolute left-[17px] top-4 bottom-12 w-px bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"flex gap-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center shrink-0\"><div class=\"w-[34px] h-[34px] rounded-full bg-white border-2 border-brand-blue flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-gold\"></div></div></div><div class=\"pb-10 pt-1.5\"><div class=\"text-[15px] font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1 leading-none\">The Founding<!-- --> <span class=\"text-brand-blue font-semibold text-[13px] ml-2\">2025</span></div><div class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed\">Sanjivani University officially establishes the football program and begins the recruitment of its first squad.</div></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center shrink-0\"><div class=\"w-[34px] h-[34px] rounded-full bg-white border-2 border-brand-blue flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-gold\"></div></div></div><div class=\"pb-10 pt-1.5\"><div class=\"text-[15px] font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1 leading-none\">Official Launch<!-- --> <span class=\"text-brand-blue font-semibold text-[13px] ml-2\">2026</span></div><div class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed\">The club enters the competitive arena, ready to set the benchmark for university football.</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-200 py-20 px-4 shadow-inner\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center mb-16\"><div class=\"section-divider mx-auto\"></div><h2 class=\"heading-section\">Why Play for Sanjivani FC?</h2></div><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"card-hover p-8 text-center bg-white\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-5\">🚀</div><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-slate-900 tracking-wider mb-2.5\">Build a Legacy</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium text-[13px] leading-relaxed\">Be a founding member. Every goal you score and every match you win will stay in our history forever.</p></div><div class=\"card-hover p-8 text-center bg-white\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-5\">⚽</div><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-slate-900 tracking-wider mb-2.5\">Pro Coaching</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium text-[13px] leading-relaxed\">Train under professional coaches with experience at the state and national levels.</p></div><div class=\"card-hover p-8 text-center bg-white\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-5\">🏟️</div><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-slate-900 tracking-wider mb-2.5\">Premium Units</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium text-[13px] leading-relaxed\">Access top-tier university facilities, equipment, and a dedicated support team.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center\"><div class=\"bg-brand-blue rounded-[32px] p-12 md:p-16 text-white shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white/5 rounded-full -mr-32 -mt-32 blur-3xl\"></div><h2 class=\"font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-widest mb-6 relative z-10\">THE FUTURE IS YOURS</h2><p class=\"text-blue-100 text-lg font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed relative z-10\">We are building more than a team; we are building a family. If you have the passion, the grit, and the talent—then you belong on this pitch.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10\"><a href=\"/recruit\" class=\"bg-brand-gold text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase shadow-lg hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-colors\" tabindex=\"0\">Apply for Trials</a><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors\" tabindex=\"0\">Contact Coaching Staff</a></div></div></section></div><!--/$--></div></main><footer class=\"bg-brand-blue-dark border-t border-white/10 mt-auto\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-14\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-brand-gold rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue-dark\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div><div class=\"font-display text-xl tracking-wider text-white\">SANJIVANI FC</div><div class=\"text-[9px] text-brand-gold/70 tracking-widest uppercase\">University Football Club</div></div></div><p class=\"text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\">Representing Sanjivani University with pride, passion, and performance. Est. 2015. Blue &amp; Gold forever.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\"><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Instagram\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white/8 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-brand-gold hover:border-brand-gold text-white/60 hover:text-brand-blue-dark transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-md\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-instagram w-4 h-4\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"20\" x=\"2\" y=\"2\" rx=\"5\" ry=\"5\"></rect><path d=\"M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z\"></path><line x1=\"17.5\" x2=\"17.51\" y1=\"6.5\" y2=\"6.5\"></line></svg></a><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Twitter\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white/8 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-brand-gold hover:border-brand-gold text-white/60 hover:text-brand-blue-dark transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-md\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-twitter w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.